    "project_template_level_name": "CSA U2L8-Operators PBT_alt-2025",
    "teacher_markdown": "The `while loop` is configured to print the `%10` (modulo 10) of the last digit and then remove it. Adding in the code snippet will print the following to the console:\r\n\r\n```\r\nOriginal number: 12345\r\nExtracted Digit: 5\r\nExtracted Digit: 4\r\nExtracted Digit: 3\r\nExtracted Digit: 2\r\nExtracted Digit: 1\r\n```",
